text: Lynelle Kugler (born November 13, 1981) is an American rugby union player. She played for the University of Northern Colorado. She played for the United States at the 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup. == References == == Other websites == * Rugby Interview: USA Legend Phaidra Knight & USA Star Lynelle Kugler, rugbywrapup.com May 22, 2012 * Lynelle Kugler of the USA charges upfield zimbio Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:American rugby union players
